examples.en: In school classmates ganged on / against him.
All of your classmates have begun their projects, and I suggest you do the same.
The teacher assigned him to lead his classmates in the exercise.
The girl's classmates were bullying her online, sending her hateful e-mails and text messages.
He reached puberty later than most of his classmates.
She was cunning enough to beguile her classmates into doing the work for her.
She had such maternity at such a young age that all her classmates went to her for comfort.
